          </div>
          <div class="metric-card">
            <div class="metric-number">51</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Domain rating (from 0)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-card">
            <div class="metric-number">8K+</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Developer community built</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-card">
            <div class="metric-number">5</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Launch Weeks</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="cv-section">
        <h2><span class="emoji">üíº</span> My recent rides</h2>
        
        <div class="experience-item">
          <div class="experience-header">
            <div>
              <span class="role-title">Head of Growth</span> at <span class="company">Daytona</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2023-2025</span>
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>Led entire PLG and GTM strategy for developer tools startup competing with GitHub Codespaces, Gitpod, and Coder</li>
